            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 上星期举行了发布会，席间公布了 iPhone 16 及 16 Pro 系列、全新 AirPods 4 主动降噪版、Apple Watch Series 10、Apple Watch Ultra 2 黑色钛金属版等，以及全新手机套和 MagSafe 配件等。今日起全部秋季新产品已登陆香港全线 6 间 Apple Store ，有兴趣看看实物的朋友可以亲临各 Apple Store。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264449" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8275-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8275-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8275.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲iPhone 16 全颜色已登陆 Apple Store</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264450" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8276-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8276-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8276.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲iPhone 16 Pro 四款钛金属色亦已于 Apple Store 展出</p><p>Apple Intelligence 将于 10 月随 iOS 18.1、iPad 18.1 与 macOS Sequoia 15.1 一并推出，更多功能亦紧随数月内登场。此为将生成模型的强劲效能与个人背景相结合的的个人智能系统，为用户带来极为实用且相关的智能功能。</p><p>Apple Intelligence 率先推出美国英文版，并将于明年扩展至更多语言，包括中文、日文、韩文。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264451" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8278-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8278-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8278.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全新 Apple Watch Series 10</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1264452" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8279-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8279-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/img_8279.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全面采用 USB-C 的 5 款新颜色 AirPods Max 亦已于 Apple Store 展出<br />
（午夜黑、蓝色、紫色、橙色和星光金）</p><p>下面为 Apple 用家到访 Apple Store 试玩新 iPhone 16、iPhone 16 Pro 系列手机的盛况：</p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="Apple Store 20 Sep 2024-1" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1011243091?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="Apple Store 20 Sep 2024-2" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1011243126?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><div style="padding: 56.25% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_8273" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1011243152?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/07/apple-store-hints-at-iphone-16-release-date/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">瑞典 Apple Store 公布开业安排，被指配合 iPhone 16 系列首卖日</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/21/apple-kuala-lumpur-store/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Store 终于登陆马来西亚   Apple 吉隆坡店明日开幕</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/20/apple-2024-fall-items-all-iphone-16-in-apple-store-now/software/ios-app/">香港 Apple 秋季新产品今日开卖　iPhone 16 全颜色、AirPod 4 陈列品登陆全线 Apple Store</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
